@startuml
actor Cliente
participant PaymentController
participant PaymentService

== Happy Path ==
Cliente -> PaymentController : POST /payments/upload
PaymentController -> PaymentService : uploadPayment(request)
PaymentService -> PaymentService : valida userId y fileUrl
PaymentService -> PaymentService : crea Payment PENDING
PaymentService --> PaymentController : PaymentResponse OK
PaymentController --> Cliente : 200 - Comprobante subido

== Error - datos faltantes ==
Cliente -> PaymentController : POST /payments/upload
PaymentController -> PaymentService : uploadPayment(request)
PaymentService -> PaymentService : lanza BusinessException
PaymentService --> PaymentController : GlobalExceptionHandler
PaymentController --> Cliente : 400 - mensaje de error
@enduml